{"title": "Galatians: God's Answer to Legalism", "description": "A brief outline and commentary on the New Testament Book of Galatians. \"The epistle to the Romans presents the foundation truth of justification provided only by the grace of God and received only by faith. Corinthians comes next with instructions against <b>practical</b> error in this truth. Galatians follows with instructions against <b>doctrinal</b> error in the same truth. Therefore, in Galatians, law vs. grace and works vs. faith are the prominent features.\" - Summary by Author", "duration": 4074, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "17413", "name": "B. B. Sutcliffe"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/galatians_2304_librivox/galatiansgodsanswer_2304.jpg", "copyright_year": "1922", "genres": ["Christianity - Commentary"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "3rdAnchor"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "3rdAnchor"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "mleigh"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Galatians: God's Answer to Legalism -Introduction - Galatians 1:1-10", "readers": [18306], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/galatians_2304_librivox/galatiansgodsanswer_00_sutcliffe_64kb.mp3", "duration": 664}, {"section": 1, "title": "I. Personal - Galatians 1:11-2:21", "readers": [18306], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/galatians_2304_librivox/galatiansgodsanswer_01_sutcliffe_64kb.mp3", "duration": 582}, {"section": 2, "title": "II. Doctrinal  - Galatians 3:1-4:31", "readers": [18306], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/galatians_2304_librivox/galatiansgodsanswer_02_sutcliffe_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1628}, {"section": 3, "title": "III. Practical - Galatians 5:1 - 6:16", "readers": [18306], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/galatians_2304_librivox/galatiansgodsanswer_03_sutcliffe_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1135}, {"section": 4, "title": "Conclusion: Galatians 6: 17-18", "readers": [18306], "path":